inn1.comm: gentle loosener to start with, but it takes off from a length and Akmal takes it in front of his face.
again outside off, moves away from the batsman and Gambhir leaves it alone
short of length on the off stump, it gets up on the batsman who has to hop to defend it down the pitch
fuller length outside off, and it's left alone, but guess where Akmal takes it - yes, in front of his face again
length ball on off stump, Gambhir goes back and drops it down
back of length on off, Gambhir goes back and again defends it down the pitch.
starts with a no-ball, and it's a free hit
it is bowled on the pads and Sehwag is unable to get any bat on it, hits him and rolls to Irfan at fine leg
pitches on length and on leg stump, Sehwag just flicks it in front of square to the boundary at midwicket
lovely delivery now! This one goes away with the angle and Sehwag is only half forward, gets beaten by the ball
on the pads again, some swing and it hits Sehwag on the pads again. The batsmen take a leg-bye but Sehwag missed on some runs there.
fuller length wide outside off and Gambhir goes for a drive, gets beaten as he plays outside the line of the ball
length ball on the middle and Gambhir wanted to flick it towards leg-side, but gets a leading edge towards cover
attempts a yorker first-up, but it's down the leg side and Sehwag gets hit on the pads and the ball rolls to fine-leg
full and wide outside off, Gambhir stretches out and drives it in the air between point and gully for a couple
length ball on the middle, Gambhir pushes it towards the vacant midwicket area for another couple
a corker! It was length ball bowled with an angle, Gambhir goes forward in defence but the ball just leaves him a touch at the last moment
edged to the third-man boundary! short of length outside off and Gambhir goes for a cut, but the ball is too close and the ball falls just short of Younis at second slip
tries to take his bat away but gets hit anyway, the ball rolls towards second slip again
back of length delivery on off stump, not much movement, defended off the back foot towards the off side
length ball on off, Sehwag drives it on the up and with an open face to point
how close was that! It was a back of length delivery on off and Sehwag tries to take his bat away at the last moment, gets an inside edge and the ball just goes past the stumps to the keeper
big appeal for lbw! It pitched in line with stumps, comes in and hits Sehwag on the thigh pad on its way to the keeper

cleans him up now! A length delivery on the middle stump and its swings in to Sehwag, who tries to push it to cover without covering the line of the ball, the ball drives through the gap and crashed into off and middle
leaves this one alone, but it wasn't too far from the off stump
length ball outside off and Gambhir leaves it alone, good bounce again
short of length outside off, cuts away a touch but Gambhir stays patient and leaves it alone
keeps it in the channel outside off, Gambhir lets it go to the keeper

middle stump now! He was bowling it outside off consistently and now he bowls it fuller on the middle stump, Gambhir comes forward to play a loose drive, but is late on the ball, it crashes into the middle stump. Excellent set-up by Irfan there. And just like that, India are two down
short of length on the off stump, Yuvraj has to hop as he defends that towards the off side
length ball on off and Yuvraj goes on the back foot but flicks it on the leg side
beats him outside off, it's the one which carries on with the angle and Kohli comes forward but doesn't cover the line well
fuller length outside off, moves a touch away from Kohli, left alone this time
and now he brings this one back! Kohli is completely beaten as he plays outside the line, the bounce takes the ball over the off stump

off stump now! It's the big wicket. Fuller length, comes in after pitching on off, Kohli comes forward and like the previous delivery, doesn't cover the line of the ball well. He wasn't really sure of which way the ball was going to go, it comes back and hits the top of off. That's a big big wicket
back of length, comes back in and Rohit gets an inside edge! It goes past the stumps and a lucky break for Rohit

middle and off stump disturbed! Junaid is on a roll, he bowls a length ball on off stump, it just goes straight on and Yuvraj, instead of playing it straight, tries to play it towards midwicket and closes the face of the bat, gets beaten completely and India are four down.
pitches on length but outside leg, Rohit gets hit on the pads with that one
length ball outside off, goes across with the angle, Rohit lets it go through to the keeper
length ball outside off, Rohit comes forward to play a push to the off side, the ball hits the inside edge and goes back to the bowler
short of length just outside off, and it is safely left alone by Rohit
fuller delivery on the middle, swings into the batsman, Rohit blocks it out towards mid-on
short of length, angles across Rohit who lets it go through
length delivery, but going down the leg side, hits Raina on the pads, but Akmal stops some extras
length ball on off stump, Raina doesn't try to push at like others, he plays a solid defensive block
short of length on the middle, Raina goes back and tries to turn it to the leg side, gets hit on the thigh pads
short of length outside off, this leaves the batsman and Raina hangs his bat while he is on the back foot, gets beaten
short of length on the off now, Raina bring out the defensive block as he plays this one off the back foot
short of length but gets the direction wrong as this one is down the leg side, Raina hops and comes inside the line, and glances it to the fine-leg boundary.
now Umar beats Rohit outside off. It is on a length and leaves Rohit who has come forward in defence
short of length on the middle and leg, Rohit is unable to get it away as he gets hit on the pads
short of length on off, Rohit gets on top of the bounce and chops it down to third man off the back foot
back of length on off, Raina goes back to defend that but the ball hits the outside half of the bat and rolls toward point
short of length on off, Raina goes back and defends that solidly
length ball on the leg stump and Raina, who tries to play it towards square leg, gets a leading edge past point for a couple
that's more of a Test-match shot. It is a length ball on off, and Rohit punches it down the ground
pitches on middle and cuts away from the batsman by a long way. Rohit gets beaten in his defence
length ball on the middle, defended towards mid-on off the front foot

caught at third slip Another one goes down. It's a short of a length delivery on off, Rohit came forward to play at that but the ball bounces a touch extra. Rohit gets hit on the shoulder of the bat and it flies low to the right of Hafeez at third slip where he completes a tough catch very easily
length ball outside off, it is left alone. The ball comes in a bit after pitching
short of length delivery which goes away with the angle, Dhoni goes back and just pulls hit bat out of line at the last moment
length ball on the middle and Raina edges it through the vacant gully region, it goes to third-man. Raina was pushing at this one aiming towards midwicket area.
short of length outside off, Dhoni goes back but shoulders arms
testing line and length by Gul. It is closer to the stumps, just short of good length, Dhoni lets it go
length ball outside off, Dhoni takes a step down the track and tries to play it towards the leg side and gets hit on the pads. Loud appeal is turned down as he was hit outside the line of off
length ball outside off, cut away a bit, left alone by the batsman
fuller length outside off, leaves the batsman after pitching, left alone by Dhoni
fuller length outside off and Raina comes forward to crunch it to mid-off with a lot of timing
short of length on the off stump, Raina goes back and tucks it away past square leg for a couple
short of length outside off, Raina hops as he tries to defend that off the back foot, but it doesn't bounce as much. It takes an outside edge to third-man
he calls for a quick single after defending this short of length ball towards mid-off
quick short ball, 143 kph, but it's outside off and bounces way over the batsman. It has been called a wide
short of length just outside off, defended to mid-off off the back foot
defended towards the leg side off the front foot
down the leg side and it's swings away from a diving Kamran Akmal
appeals for lbw, as Dhoni is hit on the pad in his front foot defence. That hit him outside the line of off
he chips down the pitch, but the ball is wide outside off and Dhoni shoulder's his arms right at the end
length ball in the channel outside off, moves away a touch, left alone by Dhoni
short ball, but it's outside off. Dhoni shapes to pull but decides against it at the end
length ball on the off, Dhoni is quick to get into the front foot and drives it to Irfan at mid-on who allows a couple with a misfield
length ball on the off and middle line, Dhoni closes the face of the bat on that one, gets it between midwicket and square leg for another couple
fuller ball down the leg side and it's an easy decision for the umpire
short of length on the pads, Raina hops and dabs it to the left of square leg for a single
short of length outside off, goes away with the angle, Dhoni lets it go through to the keeper
length ball on the middle and leg, Dhoni goes back and across and pushes it through midwicket for a couple
short of length on off and Dhoni goes back across again, plays it down to fine-leg for a single
short of length on the middle, Raina goes back and turns it fine on the leg side to bring up the team's fifty
short of length, pitches on middle and goes across Dhoni with the angle, the batsman lets it go
length ball on off, Raina gets right behind the line and defends it down the pitch
length ball, pitches on leg and hits the batsman on the pads as he tries to get across, it rolls to the fine-leg boundary for more extras
short of length on off, defended towards mid-off off the back foot
short ball on the middle, Raina hops and gets on top of the bounce to turn it to fine-leg
short of length outside off, punched to cover off the back foot
bowls length on off, Raina comes forward positively and punches it through extra cover, the outfield is slow and the ball is pulled back before it gets to the boundary
short of length on off, Raina defends it off the back foot
another one just short of length, it gets up on the batsman, Raina defends it off the back foot
gets width outside off and that helps him guide the ball to third-man for a single
short-ish ball on the middle, Dhoni tries to pull but is hurried in his shot because of the pace, can only get it to square leg
full ball down the leg side, and it's not called a wide.
short of length on the body, Raina dabs it towards midwicket and sets off for a quick single
short of length outside off, Raina goes back when he should have gone forward, the ball doesn't bounce as much and he edges it towards second slip, luckily for him, it didn't carry
back of length outside off, pushed off the back foot towards cover
defended back to the bowler off the back foot and Umar Gul fires a throw past Raina.
bowls a short ball, Raina pulls it towards deep backward square, rolling his wrists on that shot
length ball on off, Dhoni turns it to midwicket
short of length outside off, defended towards cover off the back foot
back of length delivery on the pads, gets hit on the pads and it goes towards short fine leg
length ball on the pads, and it is another leg-bye
short of length on off stump, Raina goes back and turns it to deep square leg
length ball on off, Dhoni pushes it towards mid-off with soft hands and calls for a quick single
length ball outside off, goes straight on and Raina leaves it alone
short of length on off, defended solidly by Raina
on the pads and it is turned to the right of square leg for a single
flighted delivery on off, Raina comes forward and drives it down the ground to long-off
more flight, it is outside off and Dhoni defends it down the pitch
pushed through on the off and middle, Dhoni plays it to midwicket with the turn
quicker, flatter delivery, defended off the back foot
another one pushed through to the batsman, Dhoni goes back and defends it back to the bowler
full and flat on off, driven back to the bowler
flighted and Raina makes it a full-toss as he charges down, plays it in the gap without any timing towards deep midwicket
flatter delivery on the off, pushed to long-on off the back foot
flighted delivery on off, Raina comes forward in defence
grips and turns past the edge. It was flighted on off and Raina gets beaten in his defence.
floated up to the batsman who drives it to long-on
plays this towards short third-man off the back foot
flighted delivery on off, Raina defends it towards cover off the front foot
it is floated outside off and Raina lets this one go
comes forward to defend it towards the off side
flighted on the middle and Raina defends it again, gets an inside edge on to the pads
tossed up on the middle stump line, defended towards the leg side off the front foot
fuller ball on the off, Dhoni turns it to midwicket where Umar Akmal, the sub, prevents a single
bowls it down the leg side, Dhoni gets some bat towards square leg and looks for a single, but is sent back
pushed to midicket off the front foot
he pushes it back to the bowler this time
comes to the front foot and plays it to midwicket
flatter delivery, spins into Dhoni who gets hit on the thigh pad as he tries to turn this to the leg side
short and outside off, Raina goes back and cuts it past point for a boundary do bring the fifty of the partnership
full and flighted, driven back down the ground and it hits Dhoni along its way to long-on
flatter delivery on off, played towards the off side off the back foot
tossed up and full in length on the middle, Dhoni gets hit on the pads as he tries to turn it to the leg side
flatter delivery, defended off the back foot
comes forward and gets hit on the glove as the ball bounces a little more than his anticipation
beaten as he tries to push this flatter delivery off the back foot
pushed through on the off stump, defended off the back foot
fuller length on the pads, defended down the pitch
slower through the air, on the off, defended down the wicket
comes down the track but has to defend as the ball is short
flighted delivery on the middle and leg line, Raina wanted to slog-sweep this out of the ground but gets an inside edge. Another maiden
pushed through on off, turned towards midwicket for a single
flatter and on the middle, defended off the front foot
flighted outside off, Raina comes forward and pushes it to deep cover for a single
another flatter delivery, Dhoni plays it towards square leg
pushed through outside off, Dhoni punches it to cover off the back foot and takes off for a quick single
flighted delivery on off, Raina comes forward to defend it down the ground
flatter on the middle stump line, turned to midwicket
Dropped by Misbah! Dhoni comes down the ground and punches it straight to Misbah at midwicket, who palms it over his head
quicker delivery on off, Raina defends off the back foot
this one grips and bounces to the keeper, Raina takes his bat away at the last moment
comes forward and punches it to long-off
flighted delivery on off, Dhoni comes forward and defends it back to the bowler
bowls it short and flat outside off, Raina cuts it hard to deep point
short and this one spins down the leg side
flighted delivery, Dhoni comes forward and pushes it to long-on
flighted on off, defended back to the bowler off the front foot
on the pads and Raina is not able to get it away, gets hit on the front pad
looks to make a move down the pitch, but stays back and steers it to point
flighted on the middle, defended back to the bowler
flatter delivery on the pads, turned to midwicket
comes down the wicket, but Hafeez adjusts his length and Dhoni gets hit on the pads
pushed through a bit quicker, punched back to the bowler
goes back and pushes it down to long-off for a single
Raina continues to defend, this one is done off the front foot
pushed off the front foot towards extra cover where Misbah doesn't stop cleanly and allows a single
goes back and cuts it hard, but straight to point
slower through the air, on the middle, defended back to the bowler
bowls it on the leg stump, Raina goes back and whips it to deep midwicket for a single
flat, quick and short, Dhoni is unable to get it away as it spins in to him
fuller length, driven to long-on off the front foot
flatter delivery, Raina looks to come down, but stays back in the end, cuts it to point
flat and on off, pushed to midwicket off the back foot
comes down the pitch, and defends it towards the leg side
pushed through on the middle, Dhoni turns it to square leg
flighted delivery on the middle and Raina doesn't get hold of this as he goes for the slog-sweep, the ball rolls to deep midwicket boundary
comes forward in defence, but that takes outside edge to short third-man
flatter and shorter on off, Raina goes back and punches it to deep cover off the back foot
short and it spins away, Raina has to stretch out and gets a toe end on that towards cover
fuller length, driven hard to mid-on off the front foot
flat and short on the middle stump, Dhoni goes back and turns it to the leg side
flatter down the leg side, Raina turns it fine on the leg side to bring up the team's 100
flighted outside off, Dhoni comes forward to drive it to mid-off
flatter delivery on off, pushed to midwicket off the front foot
quicker delivery on the pads, hurries on to Raina who defends it off the back foot
flat and on the middle, Raina gets an outside edge as he closes the face early
shorter length outside off, cut straight to point
slower through the air, this one turns past the outside edge
and gets another outside edge to short third-man, Raina not looking in control in this over
he comes down the track, but can't  beat the only fielder inside the circle on leg - mid-on
flatter and outside off, Raina gets beaten by the bounce as he goes for a cut
slower and flighted on middle, defended back to the bowler off the front foot
more flight, it's on off stump and Raina turns it to deep midwicket off the front foot
flatter on the stumps, turned to midwicket off the front foot
short and it turns into Dhoni, who plays it to square leg off the back foot
quicker through the air, driven to the left of Misbah at midwicket
makes room against this flatter delivery, but can't beat the fielder at point

bowled him! another one goes down. Raina tries to hoick this quicker delivery towards his favoured midwicket boundary, but the ball hurries on to him and knocks the leg stump back. Dhoni is disappointed with that shot as it was only the second Powerplay delivery. Pakistan make a breakthrough after 23 overs.
flighted on off, the batsman drives it back to the bowler
slower and on a length, Ashwin goes back and punches it to long-on
flatter delivery on the middle, turned to midwicket
plays this one with soft hands to the right of Misbah at midwicket to keep the strike
pushed on the leg stump, Dhoni plays it straight to square leg
on the middle stump, Dhoni can't beat the inner ring around midwicket area
pushes this to point off the back foot to take a single
bowls the doosra to Ashwin, the batsman defends it down the pitch
quicker delivery on the stumps, turned to square leg off the back foot
flighted outside off, defended towards point off the front foot
charges down the track, but doesn't get everything behind it. It lands just a couple of yards inside the boundary  around cow corner, the ball stops on the outfield
pushed to mid-off with soft hands for a single
quicker delivery outside off, defended off the front foot
comes down the pitch, it is short and quick and is defended back to the bowler
fuller and quicker, turned to square leg
punched down the ground to long-on
flighted on off, Ashwin drives it to long-on off the front foot
flatter delivery on the middle, turned to square leg off the back foot
quicker and on off stump, Dhoni goes back and punches it hard to deep cover, Azhar Ali attempts a slide but his knee gets stuck, and he seems to have twisted his back along the way.
flighted outside off, Ashwin gets an outside edge past slip as he attempts to drive that one through cover
drives this one off the front foot nicely, through cover. Irfan is too slow to run around that from mid-off, and now he has done some damage to his hamstring. He is leaving the field for now
punched off the back foot towards the leg side
full toss on the pads, flicked away to deep square leg for a single
he comes down the track and drives the ball down to long-on
flighted outside off, Dhoni pushes it to mid-off who is a bit deep for a single
stays back and punches this flatter delivery for another single to long-on
fuller length on off, Dhoni pushes it to long-on
punched off the front foot down to long-on for another single
length ball outside off, driven on the up to deep cover
short of length on off, defended back to the bowler off the back foot
back of length on off, defended towards the leg side
short ball and Dhoni brings out the pull, but he can't beat the fielder at deep backward square
he pulls it in front of square comfortably of a short ball
another short ball and this time Dhoni finds that gap at deep backward square. Two fielders were converging on that one, but the ball beats both to the boundary
length ball on the middle stump line, defended towards midwicket and the batsmen call for a quick single
short of length on off, Dhoni hits it past point off the outside half of his bat, and the bowler has overstepped.
a length ball and Dhoni gets under it, powers it down the ground over the long-on boundary for the first six of the match
length ball on the pads, it's flicked to short fine leg and Umar Gul makes a good stop and fires a throw back to the stumps. Dhoni was gone had this one hit as he was sent back by Ashwin
square-driven to deep point off the front foot
length ball outside off, pushed to cover off the front foot
down the leg side and it is an easy call for the umpire
short ball, Dhoni quickly gets into the position to play a swivel-pull and plays it fine to Umar Gul at fine-leg to  keep the strike
short of length outside off, Dhoni gets beaten with the bounce
fuller ball on the middle, and he flicks it over midwicket to the cow-corner boundary, that shot was played with a lot of bottom hand and it brings up his fifty
short of length ball, he gets an inside edge on to his pads, the ball gets stuck in his right pad
another back of length delivery, punched to extra cover off the back foot
short of length delivery on off, pushed to cover off the back foot
another short of length delivery on off, pushed to cover off the back foot and the batsmen call for a quick single
turned to midwicket off the front foot
on the pads, it is turned to deep square leg
slow and flighted on the off, defended down the pitch
on the pads, it is turned to the left of short fine-leg for a single
punched to mid-off off the back foot for a single, the fielder is standing on the edge of the circle
takes a couple of steps, but plays this quicker delivery back to the bowler
length ball and Dhoni gives it a might heave, doesn't connect at all. Wonder what drink did he just have. That shot came from nowhere
attempts another lofted shot over long on but gets an outside edge to third-man for a single
length ball on off, the batsman defends it back to the bowler
length ball on off, but Ashwin walks across the stumps to flick it past short fine-leg for a couple
attempts a yorker, but it's a full-toss and it's easily flicked away to deep square leg
takes a step out and cuts this length ball outside off to third-man
flatter on the pads, it is flicked to short fine leg for a single
punched to long-off off the back foot
flighted on the middle, Dhoni tries to loft it straight down, but gets it over extra cover off the outside half of the bat
stays in the crease and turns this delivery to square leg for a single
fuller delivery, 91 kph, driven down the ground to long-on
flighted delivery on the pads, turned to deep square leg
short ball, and pulled powerfully in front of square for a boundary
short of length on off, Dhoni dabs it to point and takes off for a quick single
short ball outside off, Ashwin tries to play an upper cut, but gets a toe-end to third man
another short ball outside off and Dhoni just hangs his bat at that, gets a top edge that shorts just short of the fielder running in from third-man
he takes a quick single with a push to mid-off
back of length and Dhoni plays it towards cover with soft hands for another quick single
flatter delivery from round the stumps, turned to square leg for a single
comes down the track, but gets hit on the pads off this quicker delivery, it rolls towards short fine-leg

he finds some energy to send this flighted delivery soaring over the long-on boundary. It is a long long hit, way up into the stands. The umpires have asked for a replacement ball as this has gone out of the ground.
flatter and on the middle, pushed back to the bowler
quicker delivery on the pads, played to square leg with soft hands for a single
comes down charging, but the ball is quick and flat, Ashwin gets hit on the pads
short ball and Dhoni goes for his killer pull, but it takes an outside edge and that goes past point for a boundary. Everyone was looking towards the leg side..
another short ball outside off, and he plays the tennis forehand past mid-off for some runs, the ball gets pulled up just inside the boundary
yorker on off, he attempts the helicopter shot but can only get it as far as midwicket
length ball, goes away with the angle and Ashwin gets beaten as he tries to steer this to third-man off the back foot
length ball, Ashwin opens up his stance to smash it over the bowler's head, gets a top-edge that goes on the bounce to third-man
short of length delivery on off, steered to third-man for an easy single
short ball and it's pulled away to deep midwicket for a single
tries the reverse-sweep off one which is on the middle, can't connect properly
comes down the track and drives it to long-off for a single
quicker delivery on the off, defended down the pitch
down the leg side, it's turned to short fine leg for a single
makes room, but the ball is bowled flat and quick at him, gets hit on the thigh pad
length ball outside off, and he drives it back down the ground with some power to bring up 200 for the team.
width outside off and Dhoni slashes it hard  to deep point boundary to bring up his 7000 runs in style. What more, it's also a 100-run partnership between these two
length ball on off, Dhoni makes room and lofts it over cover for his third six to bring up a magnificent hundred in testing conditions.
the helicopter this time, it is full ball on the middle, it is whipped to deep midwicket for a couple
good yorker , it is driven to long-on for a single.
interesting shot by Ashwin. He moves across outside off, almost near the wide marker and plays this delivery between the wide marker and the off-stump to a boundary past the keeper
short of length outside off, Dhoni swings and misses
very good yorker, Dhoni can't do much with it, but takes a single
he moves about on the crease, gets a low full-toss that is played straight to point
another yorker, it is flicked to deep square leg and the batsman calls back for a double and does it easily.
another yorker, but it's outside off and he steers it over short third-man for another boundary
full and on the blockhole, it's defended towards square leg and Dhoni calls for the double and gets it.

inn2.comm: bowls him first ball! He starts just like he did in Bangalore. It is a big inswinger from outside the off stump and Hafeez thought he was just letting a harmless delivery go, but this one came in and took the off stump out. The stumps take another battering and an excellent start for Bhuneshwar in ODI cricket

oh my! how close was that!. It was another big indipper, stays low and hits the batsman right in front of the stumps, Billy Bowden says no, Dhoni asks for a review, Bowden smiles..It probably just hit him outside the line of off
takes a couple of steps out, but this one goes straight on and is left alone
walks across the stumps, the ball is pitched on length and shapes away, defended towards the leg side
this one goes away from a length, the batsman lets it go, Dhoni takes the bails off in a flash
a loud appeal for lbw to an inswinger, the batsman is hit outside the line of off there as he takes a big forward stride
short of length on stumps, the batsman defends it down the pitch
short of length delivery on the middle, turned to square leg off the back foot for a single
short of length wide outside off, left alone by the batsman
keeps it in that channel outside off, Azhar shoulders arms
keeps it nice and straight outside off, not much movement for Ishant, left alone again
short of length outside off, Azhar watches that carefully and lets it go through
short of length outside off, Jamshed goes for the cut and gets an under edge  that is stopped by a leaping second slip
fuller length, looking for the one that comes in to the left-hander, driven to mid-on
short of length, 131.8 kph, outside off, defended off the back foot to cover
bowls an outswinger now and Jamshed gets beaten as he tries to play that from the crease. Jamshed nods in approval
another outswinger, fuller this time and beats Jamshed again. No feet movement from the batsman
makes it three in a row, another outswinger beats Jamshed as he tries to defend that from the crease
short of length outside off, defended towards point off the back foot
length ball on the stumps, defended back to the bowler
he keeps it tight in that channel outside off, testing Azhar's patience, the batsman lets it go
length ball angling in, the batsman gets an inside edge on to his pads as he tries to play it on the on side
keeps it straight, making Azhar play. The batsman defends it to mid-on
length ball outside off, Azhar takes a forward stride and guides it to third man for a single
draws an edge with a short of length delivery leaving the batsman, it just drops short of Raina at second slip
beats him outside off with another away swinger
and another one, pitches on length outside off, drawing Azhar forward and then beating him in his forward prod
keeps it there and Azhar decides against playing a shot this time, lets it go
outswinging delivery outside off, Azhar comes forward and plays it towards point
there comes the inswinger, but the length is shorter and it allows the batsman to flick it away to square leg off the back foot
length ball, shaping into the left-handed Jamshed, defended to the off side from the crease
quicker delivery, bounces extra from short of length, Jamshed slashes and gets beaten
short of length, 137 kph, on the off stump line, the batsman goes back and defends it down the pitch
short of length delivery on off, and Jamshed punches it to the left of mid-on with lovely timing, Ishant dives but doesn't stop it cleanly
back of a length delivery on the pads, Azhar stays back and whips it to fine-leg easily
back of length and on middle stump, punched to mid-on
defended off the front foot towards cover, the ball was bowled short of length on off
bowls a quick short one, 137 kph, as he sees Azhar walking down the pitch, the batsman sways out of line at the last minute
walks across the stumps and defends this short of length delivery to the leg side
walks across again and pushes for a single by dabbing it to mid-off
another short ball, 137.7 kph, Jamshed gets under that one easily and lets it go.
bowls an away swinger to beat Jamshed in his defence to finish the over
bowls this one on the leg side and it is flicked away to deep backward square leg for a couple
an outswinger that pitches outside off and goes further away, left alone by the batsman
short of length outside off, punched to mid-off off the back foot
back of length on off stump, the batsman hops and gets behind that one to defend it on the off side
gets the ball to move away from a short of length, left alone by the batsman
another back of a length delivery, Azhar defends it off the back foot
back of length on off stump, Jamshed stays back and whips it to midwicket
takes a couple of steps down and turns the ball to the leg side
length ball on the middle, not much swing there, driven to mid-on with timing
again comes a step down the track, punches the length ball to mid-off
short of length on middle, turned to deep backward square for a single
length ball on the middle stump line, driven straight to mid-on this time. Jamshed getting a bit more comfortable against Bhuvneshwar now
short of length outside off, punched to cover off the back foot
walks across and dabs this short of length ball to gully and takes off for a single. Raina from second slip makes a diving stop
length ball on off, gets an inside edge towards midwicket for a single
short ball outside off, it goes high over the head and is signalled a wide
short of length, dabbed to point, Azhar thinks about a single but is rightly sent back as the ball very close to Kohli at point
short of length outside off, tries to punch it towards off, gets an outside edge to third-man
short of length on off, Jamshed comes forward to defend that down the pitch

big misunderstanding and a missed run out chance! Azhar Ali gets hit on the pads and Jamshed comes all the way to the other end, the bowler gets there first and tries, has all the time to aim and hit at the non-striker's but misses. Life for Jamshed

caught at midwicket! No life for Azhar though. It was a short delivery outside off and Azhar tries to drag it towards the on side, doesn't get any timing and he is not really in balance as he plays that shot, the ball lobs up tamely to Rohit Sharma at midwicket. Bhuvi gets his second
length ball on off, not much swing there, defended from the crease by Younis to the off side
fuller delivery wide outside off, moves away a touch, Younis takes a big stride and lets it go
short of length outside off, punched straight to cover off the back foot
finishes the over off with a short ball, not a problem for Younis though, he gets comfortably out of the way
length ball with width, Jamshed drives it in the air towards cover, gets to a diving Kohli on the bounce. He saves some runs there
short of length on off, bounces extra, Younis gets firmly behind that as he defends it towards point
short of length on off stump again, defended solidly towards cover
tries to steer the short of length delivery to third-man, but Raina at gully cuts down the single
length ball on off and Younis allows the ball to come on to him, and opens the face right at the end to find the gap between Sehwag at first slip and gully

short and wide, cut hard over point, but the outfield is slow. Bhuvi gets time to run around from third man and keep the batsmen to two. There was almost a chance of a run out as the batsmen think of a third
length ball outside off, 133.4 kph, defended off the front foot towards cover
keeps it on length on off, punched to cover off the front foot
short of length on the middle, the batsman gets an inside edge towards square leg
length ball, Jamshed comes down the track and drives it making room outside off, but hits it straight to the man at mid-off
short of length with some width, Jamshed is upset for not finding the  boundary with that one. He got behind that, but hit it straight to point
short ball on the leg side, Jamshed swivels in a flash to send it to fine-leg boundary
short of length on off, defended back to the bowler
gets some width outside off and Younis punches it in the gap at cover, the outfield slows the ball down
length ball on off, driven firmly to short cover who turns and has a shy at non-striker's. Hits Younis' bat
short ball on the middle, Jamshed gets into a good position and pulls it to fine leg again
short ball wide outside off, but Younis pulls it from there over midwicket, doesn't get much timing but it goes safely over the infield
short of length outside off, steered to point
beautifully timed through cover. It was a length ball angling away, Jamshed drives it from the crease with just timing and it races away on the slow outfield
length ball on off, pushed to mid-off and Jamshed calls for a quick single, Bhuvi has a shy and that could have been close had he hit
short of length, but wide and Younis slashes at it to hit it towards third-man
on the pads and it is turned away to fine leg easily for a single
fuller length ball on off, and it's driven back in the air towards the bowler, who ducks under it for some reason. He could have taken that. He must have misjudged the speed on that ball
short of length outside off, punched to cover off the back foot
flatter delivery on the middle and leg, pushed to midwicket off the back foot
keeps it on the off and middle line, turned to square leg off the back foot
flighted delivery outside off, Younis gets an outside edge as he tries to play it towards midwicket
tossed up outside off, dabbed to the off side, Sehwag runs around quickly from first slip to cut off the single
bowls it on the pads, Younis turns it to square leg
flighted outside off, the batsman comes forward to defend it down the pitch
flights this one on the middle, driven back to the bowler
slower through the air, outside off, punched back to the bowler off the back foot
tossed up on off stump, Jamshed drives it hard to long-on
gives it a lot of air outside off, Younis carves it to deep cover
flighted on off, wristily driven to long-on off the front foot
flatter delivery, shorter in length too, Younis gets down on his knees and drags it on the leg side, in front of square for a couple

flighted ball on the middle, the ball hits the pads and is taken by Sehwag, bowler appeals for lbw and then for the catch. Umpire not interested. It was an inside edge, but no one apart from Ashwin appealed
flatter delivery on middle and off, whipped to square leg
flatter delivery on the middle, gets an inside edge on to the pads
flighted delivery on the middle, the batsman gets inside the line and flicks it to fine leg
hits the bat and then the pad with one directed down the leg side, it rolls towards the leg side and the batsmen run
slider going across the bat, beats Jamshed's outside edge
slower delivery, Jamshed waits for it, goes back and then punches it hard through cover
flighted down the leg side, swept away to fine leg for a single
now Younis sweeps. He gets a big stride out and gets it to deep backward square
stays back and punches it to the right of extra cover for a single
flatter and shorter on the middle, Younis pulls it to deep midwicket for another single
flatter delivery on off, turns in a bit, Younis punches it to long-on easily
angles this one on the pads, Jamshed unable to get it away
flighted on off stump, the batsman comes forward to drive it to long-off
on the leg side, Younis gets inside the line and turns it to deep backward square
pushed through on off stump line, defended back to the bowler
slower and flighted on middle and leg, defended back to the bowler
tries to sweep it from wide outside off, gets beaten as the ball turns away
goes back to this slow, flighted ball and punches it to deep cover easily
flighted, and almost a yorker, blocked back to the bowler
gives it a lot of air, the batsman drives hard past a diving midwicket for a single
flatter delivery on the middle, defended to the leg side
floated on the off and middle line, the batsman plays it to midwicket from the inside half of the bat
sweeps again and in the air, nicely into the gap at deep backward square. Ishant from fine leg comes across to cut it off
flatter delivery on off, turned to midwicket
short and wide, it was cruched to cover where Gambhir makes a good stop
goes back to a delivery that he shouldn't have, gets an inside edge past stumps towards short fine leg
flatter delivery, hits Jamshed on the pads as he goes down to play the paddle, that was going down the leg side
shortish ball, comes slow off the surface, the batsman pull is in the air towards long-on
short ball,  pushes it to short midwicket
goes back again, and again finds Sehwag at short midwicket
waits for the ball to come to him and turns it to fine leg with the spin
floated outside off, Younis waits and then pushes it to deep cover
comes down the track to a full-toss, whacks it down to deep midwicket boundary
quicker delivery on the middle, flicked away to square leg for a single
flighted delivery on the middle, defended down the pitch
pushes the flatter delivery to the left of Ashwin, who makes a good one-handed stop
quicker delivery outside off, the batsman gets hurried as he plays that one on the off side
flighted up to the batsman, driven down the ground to long-on
drifting on to the pads, no turn, as the batsman gets hit on the pads
flighted outside off, it is driven with timing to deep extra cover. Dinda pulls the ball back at the boundary
flighted delivery on the off, pushes it to cover off the back foot
slow and on a length, Jamshed waits and flicks it to square leg for a single
flighted and full on off stump, defended down the pitch
short and on the off, Younis pulls it over mid-on and gets to the boundary even though he didn't get any timing into that
now he finds the gap at deep backward square with a powerful sweep, Gambhir makes a diving effort in vain
more runs on the off side this time as he beats the short third-man with a cut
on the pads and it is flicked hard to the shin of the fielder at forward short leg
flatter delivery on off stump, punched easily to long-off to bring up the 100 for Pakistan
pushed through on off stump, defended off the front foot
the delayed-delivery from Ashwin is swept to deep backward square leg easily
tossed up on off and middle, defended off the front foot to the leg side
flatter delivery, punched back to the bowler
flatter down the leg side, and Younis' flick almost carries to square leg
flatter on the pads, swept to fine-leg easily for a single
full and on the off, driven over the infield easily for a boundary to deep extra cover
flat and short, coming in with the angle from round the stumps, the batsman pulls it in the air towards long on
flatter delivery on off, the batsman goes back and steers it to deep cover for a single
flatter on off stump, pushed to cover without any feet movement
bowls it with a pause, but Younis goes back and cuts it to deep point with ease
drifts on to the pads and is easily flicked to fine-leg to bring up his fifty.
loud shot for lbw as Younis misses his sweep shot and gets hit in front of middle and off. Very lucky there
pushed to midwicket for a single
flatter delivery angling in, whipped to midwicket
fuller length, a bit quicker too, defended to the off side
flighted and full on the off, driven to long-on off the front foot
flatter delivery, thumped to long-off
he tries a flighted delivery outside off and it's full enough for Younis to go through with a swing, it ends up over the sight screen
pushes to long-on this time to rotate the strike after the big hit
it is time for Jamshed to show his skills, he just drives the ball in the air over long-off  and it ends deep into the stands
fuller length delivery outside off, driven straight to cover
he bowls it short and wide, it is crunched to deep cover off the back foot easily
bowls it on the pads, and is helped along to fine leg, past a slow Ashwin at short fine-leg
straighter ball on the stumps, punched to long-on for a single
and another single, Younis punches it to long-on to continue milking the bowling
bowls a low full toss which is turned to square leg
another low full-toss, Kohli gets a hand to it as it's driven back to him, but it goes to long-off
short of length on off, 134 kph, punched back to the bowler who makes a good stop in his follow through
length ball on off, driven on the up to Raina at cover who has a shy at non-striker's end

attempts a yorker, it is a low full toss which is cracked to Ashwin at midwicket who is claiming a low catch. The umpires talk to each other to check on that. Ashwin took the catch and as he got up, didn't really react and gave the impression that he might have dropped it. But then he got up and looked towards Billy Bowden asking  why the hold-up. Umpire tells him to wait. The replays show that the fielder got his hands under the ball just in time. So Younis has to go
length ball outside off, Misbah comes forward and pushed it to the right of the point fielder to take a single
a quicke short one, the batsman gets into a tangle but it flies over his head and is called a wide
short ball and pulled with some timing in front of square. Sehwag at deep square leg is just a mere spectator as he just watches it go to the boundary
length ball on off, pushed to deep cover for a single
length ball outside off, pushed to long-off easily
short and outside off, and Misbah pulls it easily to the deep midwicket fence
fuller length outside off, driven to long-off for a single
another full-length delivery and Jamshed drives it to long-off easily
slightly slower and on the middle stump, turned straight to midwicket fielder
shorter in length, but on the off stump, pushed back to the bowler off the back foot
dropped by Yuvraj. It came in and it went out. It was  a length ball outside off, Jamshed drives it in the air away from the body, it goes straight to Yuvraj at point and he drops a sitter
and now he chips it over Dinda's head for a nothing shot and takes off for a single to mid-on
short of length delivery on middle, turned to deep square leg easily off the back foot
short delivery outside off, Jamshed tries to play an upper cut and gets beaten outside off. Loss of concentration or a hurry to finish the game?
length ball on off, punched to the left of mid-off for an easy single
inswinging delivery on a length, middle stump line, on-driven past the midwicket fielder for a couple
he tries to whack it on the leg side off a length delivery, gets inside edge to fine-leg
length ball on off and middle, pushed straight to midwicket
pushed to cover off the back foot
short ball, hits the batsman after hitting the bat as he attempts to pull, goes to third-man
slower delivery on a length, Jamshed opens the face to play it towards point
short delivery on the body, Jamshed controls is pull nicely to play it towards deep backward square leg
bowls it short on the body, Jamshed swivels to pull it past midwicket for a single
another quick short ball outside off and Misbah pulls it without being in control, the ball lands safely outside the ring over midwicket
short of length delivery outside off, the batsman stays in the crease and punches it to deep extra cover
fuller length outside off, not much problems for Misbah with those deliveries, easily punches it to long-on
slower bouncer which Jamshed gets beaten on, he waited and waited and played his pull, but the ball arrived after that
a quick bouncer follows the batsman, but Jamshed has been playing his pull shots well, plays it down to deep backward square fielder
takes off for a quick single to midwicket and makes it just in time. Could have been interesting if it was a direct hit
short of length, Misbah gets an inside edge to square leg as he tries to defend that ball
fuller length delivery driven to mid-off where Kohli makes a rare misfield. He just took the eyes off the ball as he came charging down
blocks a yorker to the off side and quickly takes off for a run
short of length outside off, left alone by Misbah.
length ball on off is defended towards point off the back foot
short of a length delivery on the pads, flicked to fine-leg for an easy single
short of length outside off, Misbah lets it go through to the keeper
defends this length delivery back to the bowler
opens the face to a short of length delivery outside off and plays it to point
slower bouncer, Misbah is too early in his pull and the ball hits him on his ribs after the bat has done half a lap
length ball outside off, Misbah waits and opens the face to run this past point, gets a couple by the time Ishant from third-man fields
bowls it on the pads, it is helped to short fine-leg where the fielder makes a diving stop
flatter delivery on the pads, Misbah helps it on it's way to fine leg with a paddle
another delivery drifting on the pads, swept straight to short fine leg
flatter delivery on the middle, he goes back and punches it to wide mid-on
turns in from middle stump line, dabbed to square leg
attempts a reverse sweep as the ball is outside off, but he misses as the ball goes past the edge
fuller length delivery outside off, dug out to deep cover for a single

beaten by a slower delivery! He completely missed that one and played inside the line. His off stump takes a beating. He gave that look like he never picked up the delivery. Another wicket goes down but Pakistan still in control of this match.
short ball greets Malik at the crease, but it's too high and it goes over the head easily
gets some pace behind that one and gets a leading edge from the batsman as he tries to turn it to the leg side
second short ball, but comfortably left as it is way outside off
slower ball to end the over, Malik spots that and comes forward to defend it to the off side
flighted on the middle, it is pushed to mid-on and Kohli comes in quickly and has a shy at the stumps as Malik has walked down too far
flatter delivery, Jamshed chips it in the air towards long-off. Good that he didn't get any timing into that, otherwise it would have gone straight to long-off
flatter delivery, Malik defends down the pitch
flighted delivery on the off, Malik drives it in the air and it's not very far from Ashwin
fires a quicker delivery and the batsman gets a leading edge as he tries to whip it away
turn and bounce for the bowler, Malik comes forward but gets hit on the body
bowls a low full-toss from round the wicket, is driven to wide long on where Rohit Sharma misfields
down the leg side and Ashwin's almost embarrassing dive reaps results as he gets a hand on to the ball at short fine leg
length ball on off, punched to long-on from the crease
fuller ball on the pads, played with lot of wrist towards deep midwicket
fuller delivery on the off and middle, Malik doesn't get hold of the shot as he tries to smash it to the cow corner
bowls it flat on the off, it is punched to cover off the back foot
comes down the track and takes the ball on the full to drive it down the ground to long-o n
tossed up outside off, the batsman chops it on to the off side for a single
bowls it with a pause, it is on the pads and Malik turns it to deep midwicket easily
flatter quicker delivery on the middle, turned to deep midwicket for a single
comes down the track but realises he is not to the pitch of the ball, waits and turns it towards fine leg with soft hands

another one bowled with a pause and Malik, as he goes back to play a late cut, plays it too fine, straight into the hands of Dhoni. Umpires checking for a no-ball. It looks like Ashwin has bowled a no-ball, he is on the line. And all that smile is going to get wiped off his face very soon as the umpire calls it a no-ball. What more, it's a free hit
comes down the pitch and hits the low full-toss to long-on for only a single
length ball on off stump, the batsman stays in the crease and plays a late-cut through where a first slip should have been
this one is on length and doesn't get up much, but he plays a similar shot, this time to third-man
attempts a yorker but it's down the leg side and is called a wide
slower ball and Jamshed drives it in the air, chips it towards long-on without any timing
length ball outside off, punched to cover off the front foot
short and wide and Malik misses out. Gets beaten as he tries to go for a cut

short ball and Malik goes for a pull, but he completely mistimes that and it goes towards midwicket, but Sehwag there is holding his hand out because he has lost the ball in the lights. It wouldn't have been easy, but it was a catch, even for Sehwag's standards. Another opportunity goes abegging
length ball outside off, the batsman waits and guides the ball to third-man
short of a length outside off, steered to point
slower ball on off, the batsman pushes the ball to cover
short outside off, Jamshed plays an upper-cut for an easy single to third man
tries a slower yorker, but bowls a full-toss, it is turned to deep midwicket for a single as Pakistan bring up their 200
short ball, Jamshed plays a pull which goes over midwicket, not very far again. Dinda has a frustrated look, but that wasn't really a catch, more of a mishit
yorker outside off, blocked to point for a single
short of length outside off, Jamshed stays back and pushes it to deep cover easily
bowls a low full toss, and Malik caresses it through to deep cover for another easy single
low full-toss outside off stump, Jamshed guides it to third-man
short slower-ball on the body, it comes off the pitch like a tennis ball and Malik guides it through the slip region for a boundary
a quick bouncer to follow, Malik looks to play at that first, but moves out of the way right at the end
short of length slower ball, guided straight to point
full toss outside off and Jamshed misses that one as it is slightly slower too.
fuller delivery on the off, driven down the ground and long off has to do some work to cut the boundary out
fuller length outside off, driven to deep cover
length ball with width outside off, Malik plays a square drive past point but the outfield again slows the ball and stops the boundary
slower ball to finish the over, it is driven back to the bowler
hits him on the helmet with a short one. It didn't get up as much as Jamshed expected and he took his eyes off the ball, hits him on the side and goes towards fine leg
he gets to his second hundred against India with a pull to deep midwicket off a short ball. Well played Nasir Jamshed
short and wide, cracked to deep point off the back foot, Ishant Sharma cuts off the boundary
bowls it full on off, Malik drives it hard to Raina at cover who isn't able to stop the ball cleanly, allows a single.
short ball, but it sails over the head, Jamshed gets under it comfortably
short ball, doesn't get hold of the shot, plays along the ground to miwicket
short ball, Malik takes his eyes off as it goes over his head
length ball on the pads, pushed to deep midwicket
tries to whack it hard down the ground from a length, doesn't get the timing as the ball hits the toe-end and goes towards mid-on
slower ball, Jamshed waits and plays it to cover
short ball, Jamshed swivels and plays it down to fine-leg for a single. A metre to the either side and it could have been a boundary
short of length delivery on the middle, turned to square leg for another single
short and outside off, and Shoaib Malik opens up his stance and plays a cross-court winner down to the cow-corner. Game. Set. Match to Pakistan
